1.text: Ku suwa adǝro, kasam dǝ alama kilomita 83 yeyi awa fal woson, kuru tǝma fuwo soro fulutin be mbeji.

4.text: tuwasoro luwodǝ nandi nguwulan letǝye nǝmbutun kozǝna, nankadǝro hal’kǝlanǝmbero wolwono au biya nya sawanǝmwa, kasadǝ de amgadesowa kǝltǝno nandi diyau au araskǝro wolnowo taman kamfalye-a kozǝna.

8.text: Kawu mafiye wurtǝ yukuro so dǝ awo ajabbye gǝnyi; na kǝri so dv hanglyin letǝ gǝnyima rojinmba, kuru nguwuzǝna ma dv kawu mafiyero walzǝ wurtǝ fitin.
